---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/home.css";
---

<Layout
    title="Consultologist — AI-Assisted Specialist Consults"
    description="Consults done faster, with reasoning you can stand behind. AI-assisted consult drafts with an auditable chain of thinking, built for specialist physicians."
>
    <div class="home-page">
        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <span class="section-eyebrow">Early Access</span>
                <h1 class="hero-title">
                    Get your time back. Consults done faster, with reasoning you can stand behind.
                </h1>
                <hr class="divider" />
                <div class="dialogue-group">
                    <div class="dialogue-item">
                        <span class="dialogue-speaker">Admin</span>
                        <blockquote class="dialogue-quote">
                            "Do you <strong>consent</strong> to using AI?"
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dialogue-item">
                        <span class="dialogue-speaker">Patient №1</span>
                        <blockquote class="dialogue-quote">
                            "No. How do you <strong>know</strong> that it works?"
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dialogue-item">
                        <span class="dialogue-speaker">Patient №2</span>
                        <blockquote class="dialogue-quote">
                            "How much <strong>time</strong> until I can see the doctor?"
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <hr class="divider" />
                <p class="hero-description">
                    Admin requires patient consent. Patients are skeptical how AI can know. Yet AI
                    saves time.
                </p>
                <hr class="divider" />
                <p class="hero-description">
                    Give confidence with an auditable chain of thinking. Gain time to serve more.
                </p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a class="btn-accent" href="/contact">Join the waitlist</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <img
                    src="/images/hero.webp"
                    alt="AI-assisted specialist consultation — neural network connecting clinical interfaces"
                    width="1280"
                    height="720"
                />
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features-section">
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="card feature-card">
                    <h3>Draft in seconds</h3>
                    <p>
                        Referral package in. Structured consult draft out, grounded in the clinical
                        detail of the referral.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card feature-card">
                    <h3>Review with confidence</h3>
                    <p>
                        See how the draft was reasoned — catch errors fast and sign off knowing why
                        every recommendation is there.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card feature-card">
                    <h3>Disclose with clarity</h3>
                    <p>
                        When patients ask, you have an answer and a record — not just "AI helped",
                        but exactly how and what you reviewed.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="disclosure-section">
            <div class="card disclosure-card">
                <blockquote class="disclosure-quote">
                    "AI helped draft this consultation. Your physician reviewed every
                    recommendation."
                </blockquote>
                <p class="disclosure-body">
                    Generic AI saves you time until it doesn't. One wrong answer you can't explain
                    costs you more time than you saved.
                </p>
                <p class="disclosure-body">
                    Consultologist shows its reasoning. Every output comes with an auditable chain
                    of thinking — so you can review it in seconds, not second-guess it for minutes.
                </p>
                <p class="disclosure-body">
                    Patients increasingly ask whether AI was involved in their care. With
                    Consultologist, the answer is straightforward and reassuring. You did not hand
                    off your judgment. You used a tool that showed its reasoning, reviewed it, and
                    stood behind it before it reached your patient.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="waitlist-section">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">Early Access</span>
            <h2>Built for specialist physicians</h2>
            <p class="waitlist-description">
                Join the waitlist and we'll be in touch when your specialty is available.
            </p>
            <a class="btn-accent" href="/contact">Join the waitlist</a>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>
